{"tid":537284,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"同大廈清潔阿姐發生左關係...","createTime":"2018-01-22T14:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T18:01:49.000Z","uid":44333,"like":34,"dislike":262,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"1b731575596738f217a9b6893337840ba7692148","tid":537284,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:28:36.000Z","msg":"我喺新界區一座舊工廠大廈做野，因成日有紙皮同廢鐵唔要，所以就同一個清潔阿姊熟起來。阿姊叫萍姊，佢身裁一D都唔平<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_47.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_47.gif&h=60d2baf3&s={SIZE}\" />，佢大約40尾，個樣其實好普通，黑黑實實，不過佢有時烏地身時，見到佢對奶巧很大同好濕（汗）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次當有大量紙皮時（拆貨後）我都叫佢食飯時來收（因佢可以自己賣），有時佢會帶埋飯盒來一齊食。公司成日得我一個人，又有電視同冷氣，所以佢都經常上來食飯同蛇王。<br />\n萍姊成日問我成日食自己（指食飯）-) ，唔悶咩，我話無計啦，你泥多D囉。（見佢陰陰笑）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有次食飯睇電視報財經，佢問我有無買股票，我話有，佢話想買，但唔知買乜，跟住我推介左隻（其實睇報紙）。點知仆街隻股票幾日內3嗰幾升到5蚊，佢更係開心啦（我無買扮買左）贏左幾仟蚊。遲幾日佢買佢飯盒同啤酒來，話就話多謝我，其實想攞貼士"},{"pid":"9da2771a0e0380459c59538a5f03c98e7df289cb","tid":537284,"uid":18566,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:29:45.000Z","msg":"紅威寶"},{"pid":"e20b195b50956f2a419422d39bb3b8a9c1a09f73","tid":537284,"uid":21423,"like":77,"dislike":216,"score":-139,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d76e9be2caa996241208af2867749215c35f16dc","tid":537284,"uid":5008,"like":114,"dislike":6,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:30:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老味重口味到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77d54201be317a66020d4f8c68b19a631c93e31","tid":537284,"uid":44333,"like":8,"dislike":92,"score":-84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:30:02.000Z","msg":"食飯時，佢又問我no.，我話我D係內幕貼士，唔會亂咁比人（作嘢）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，跟住佢話會對我好D,我更係食住上問佢點好D,點知佢話買埋生果比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （心想係咪你對木瓜）<br />\n「好啊，諗諗先」，佢見我冷漠回應，加2錢肉緊話，你成日搬嘢，等我幫你揼下骨啦，我即時色心頓起，冷漠回應；又好。立即用紙皮放落地下，訓直地下睇佢點按。仆街點知惡夢開始，佢當我係廢紙同爛銅，見世色不妙，立即叫停。佢見唔對路，問我係咪唔舒服，我話哽係啦，咁撚大力，按撚死我咩。我見佢話唔好意思，我食住上話，我成日比人按知點按，我幫你按先，你記住啦（扮專家同抽佢水）。跟手叫佢訓直，按二按同佢講，你件衫好濕（汗），點按？叫佢除左件衫按啦。佢諗左諗，我話按摩係咁，同埋無人睇到，佢就除左件污穢衫，除剩個肉色barbar.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbaed480dede794f3b64d3543e67366b6678156e","tid":537284,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6974069462ba7de8157dc5a0e4ed4282c8ebb935","tid":537284,"uid":90735,"like":33,"dislike":8,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"e20b195b50956f2a419422d39bb3b8a9c1a09f73","tid":537284,"uid":21423,"like":77,"dislike":216,"score":-139,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"你邊位?"},{"pid":"713c7f47a4bd7df7bdbd7e2484dedb953f34ab83","tid":537284,"uid":151774,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:32:42.000Z","msg":"又撚狗 回帶"},{"pid":"68bdda9a41d702929b77a5c4878b15c6fddb5c24","tid":537284,"uid":80461,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇發生右關係？</blockquote>你邊位?</blockquote><br />\n個清潔阿嬸囉"},{"pid":"74cefb4464f142f374c48735b06950404c2636ea","tid":537284,"uid":127272,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇發生右關係？</blockquote><br />\n冇人識你"},{"pid":"15819dede3d7ab90902259051a0aabe18f4c9f44","tid":537284,"uid":21423,"like":11,"dislike":20,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e06b2de71502864685b1ae1bc794e520bf959557","tid":537284,"uid":8867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"156580b92057e7f73b0e12e9cf2cac34910f6250","tid":537284,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:50:40.000Z","msg":"more"},{"pid":"3850499380b17f37f8781e86c1512937b0c8b618","tid":537284,"uid":12449,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:59:40.000Z","msg":"我同伯母都發生左關係<br />\n<br />\n冇圖仲學人寫甜故？"},{"pid":"ce05ff617b115664cf8683397d23ed5a0d7f221e","tid":537284,"uid":52276,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同伯母都發生左關係<br />\n<br />\n冇圖仲學人寫甜故？</blockquote><br />\n你行出門口望下倒垃圾個呀嬸咪有曬圖畫囉"},{"pid":"9767ed24a2d37cd8a4db60ac2a6b162539ed4cee","tid":537284,"uid":35815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:06:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f22a48f15894588b70f62a161d0929435c108ec0","tid":537284,"uid":35815,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:06:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f4ca55600752d4be3643f2ac75807dca0157f22","tid":537284,"uid":44333,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T00:45:31.000Z","msg":"見佢想除bar之際，我叫佢唔駛啦（扮正經，同埋我覺得女人戴住個簿洛靚D,同驚驚地佢對波好墜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），跟手先按背，按到佢鬼咁舒服，按左一陣停左，佢話按完啦，我正經答佢背部按完，佢即時180度轉身正面對住我，我扮正經地問：唔怕唔好意思咩，佢話我咁老，怕咩。其實佢對奶真係好靚（戴bar時）同好滑，靚過好多港女。跟住我用唥正經手勢幫佢按，圍住佢波邊喺咁按，見佢輕咬嘴邊，好似巧舒服。同時我話好開心同佢按，佢用吳若x語調：點解嘅？&hellip;&hellip;，我好正經地話，你皮膚好滑同身裁好好，點知佢話，你又知。譁！玩嘢呀。跟住我無答佢。正經按多一陣，我用專業囗吻同佢講：其實「乳房同乳頭」有好多穴位，按下會減低患乳癌機會（睇咸片學），佢無答我，剩係合埋眼點一點頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3e8499ab0ad55272c6c820fdc94decb64a4da9","tid":537284,"uid":85099,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T09:59:53.000Z","msg":"屌，重口味到....."},{"pid":"71953c2885f515f9648ebd23e7876a8581964886","tid":537284,"uid":145090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"繼續呀"},{"pid":"20c772d1a733e867e696cfe36155c25ca7e2304f","tid":537284,"uid":144024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:04:47.000Z","msg":"咪賭馬，快啲繼續啦"},{"pid":"ac5f565773333c14993e94689768d9423f6e8a8d","tid":537284,"uid":158601,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:05:31.000Z","msg":"屌 痴撚線重口味到...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4d57906b62595c0fd277c5e49b727105687d94","tid":537284,"uid":94088,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"睇到黑黑實實已經無再睇落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4518347b086a0b21c112240aca68ea31d162291a","tid":537284,"uid":87515,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ac5f565773333c14993e94689768d9423f6e8a8d","tid":537284,"uid":158601,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:05:31.000Z","msg":"屌 痴撚線重口味到...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"好唔爭氣地扯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6622ba3f07a406a33514e9af73170be5a5a29cb0","tid":537284,"uid":10572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ee4d0bd28410435a1af1e28a6394a9a0d6e379","tid":537284,"uid":628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:33