},{"pid":"9e885a059bb848e0d5caa742a42751c40be7a6ca","tid":537284,"uid":43897,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇發生右關係？</blockquote><br />\n咩右？<br />\n冇發生左關係？"},{"pid":"3646596c34c687e27dca510743cb2ccdcff6b17a","tid":537284,"uid":7160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:22:17.000Z","msg":"文呢 你老尾"},{"pid":"8b92b3261d12a4f3b8f97837bb36fa11d7f20b1a","tid":537284,"uid":17585,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:42:39.000Z","msg":"馬都唔賭啦，繼續。。首先我用佢件T-shirt遮住佢塊面（方便D抽水同等佢無咁怕羞），然後用正骨手勢隔住個bar用手指撩佢粒的，堅感到粒的由凸起變超凸起，見佢隻手緊握拳頭，知道時機成熟，雙手開始事無忌大，亦無徵求萍姐意願將肉色簿洛向上推，嘩一聲（心講），2隻奶因地心吸力向外擺動。講真，好很大，乳雲好?粒的好?，做清潔都keep到，好?。我雙手已大力手握2奶，初初都扮到正經，後尾都定唔順手囗定用，嘩，好香同好好味，果然係女人汗味香D，男人幾時都係臭。當我大力搓波同食奶奶後，萍姊都定唔順發出呻吟同手握我?佬，此時佢都現真身，撥開佢件臭衫，見到佢面好紅，同見到佢好似靚左（其實佢有D似&ldquo;弓梨&rdquo;）。而自己都由冷靜變左少少失控，當然少不免大車同佢幫我除褲。"},{"pid":"ea3f8281183662426bc3817b521137f0c30b769b","tid":537284,"uid":70575,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/194355_58148d6c1b6a0969ee447ff02288bab0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F194355_58148d6c1b6a0969ee447ff02288bab0.png&h=7b90990c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f25b9d1859b2568585c0fab376d6d6e1b6053510","tid":537284,"uid":17585,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:44:29.000Z","msg":"講清楚，係佢主動除我條褲，跟住我地已經進入失控狀態，我大力搓波食奶，佢亦上下chop我?佬，我都唔執輸，企左起身，而佢亦明白張開大口迎合我?佬，老實講，囗技九流流，只係識含住唔郁。我已為吊緊吹氣Mary,不過我都唔理，合閉雙眼抽送。突然間佢覺得我差唔多時（我都唔知佢點會知）佢又企身，然後自己除低條運動?褲，我更?知佢想點，我都好合作幫佢除低條阿婆底，佢隻蟹唔係好多毛，當然唔係粉紅色，不過都算正常（我唔識睇，見到唔會反左出泥同有揪?跌出泥）當然我唔會好似77兄咁食蟹同叫佢?尿啦，我用手指撩佢，係有D濕，此時佢用手撥開我隻手，唔通佢唔想！唔向左走向右走係嘩，原來佢覺得用手指整得佢好癢，哦。。突然跟住佢好主動自己坐?寫字?度同腿張開，然後用手粗暴拉我?佬，當佢想進一步動作，這時我都按停佢：萍姊，無套啊，駛唔駛落7仔買呀！"},{"pid":"fe2de6e600c567eca38744d3410d65c293410aad","tid":537284,"uid":75156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/194355_58148d6c1b6a0969ee447ff02288bab0.png[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F194355_58148d6c1b6a0969ee447ff02288bab0.png%5Bimg%5D&d=k3FtystjW27N0V0sEM17sghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=458bc776\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/194355_58148d6c1b6a0969ee447ff02288bab0.png[img]</a></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母 佢食屎？"},{"pid":"cec89e452d9e250477d1c156d148370ff77a9822","tid":537284,"uid":8773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下你點繼續吹"},{"pid":"f12313f731751d313a092ef3a5ddf2b33f288a63","tid":537284,"uid":129470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:58:16.000Z","msg":"好重口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de98ce824ad3bb9f1c6325c051a552c772f340f6","tid":537284,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c044313532a042984a247827b8b9df14c3adeba","tid":537284,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:24:18.000Z","msg":"睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重口味到"},{"pid":"127cab939ebe9cb3caa62fe926a04b4d8ca2b7d8","tid":537284,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202c92ddfb98bd7da7cb249bccecbb34a0f56fed","tid":537284,"uid":23364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"OLD NEW IS"},{"pid":"85dcb4f